  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized, prospective, controlled open label clinical trial aimed at investigating if the&#xD;
      addition of inhaled corticosteroids (budesonide) reduces treatment failure (defined as a&#xD;
      composite variable by the initiation of treatment with high flow-O2 therapy, non-invasive or&#xD;
      invasive ventilation, systemic steroids, use of biologics (anti IL-6 or anti IL-1) and/or&#xD;
      death) according to hospital standard of care guidance) at day 15 after initiation of&#xD;
      therapeutic intervention.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
